<a name="0.1_location"></a><h2>Locations and Addresses</h2>
<ul><li><a href="http://www.allsouls-stonybrook.org/" target="_blank">All Souls Episcopal Church</a>: next to 81 Main St, Stony Brook, Suffolk, New York 11790
</li><li><a href="http://www.oldfieldclub.com/" target="_blank">The Old Field Club</a>: 86 W Meadow Rd, Setauket, New York 11733
<br><br>
All Souls' Episcopal Church is 50 miles (80.5 km) north-east from JFK
airport on long island. Old Field Club is 3 miles (6 km) north of All
Souls' Church. Both are near Long Island Sound to their west.
</li></ul>

<a name="0.1_transportation"></a><h2>Transportation</h2>
<ul>
<h3>To Stony Brook</h3>
<ul>
<li>Driving: <a href="http://maps.google.com/maps?f=d&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;saddr=JFK&amp;daddr=81+Main+St.+Stony+Brook,+NY+11790+to:40.946746,-73.13899&amp;mrcr=1&amp;mrsp=2&amp;sz=15&amp;mra=mi&amp;sll=40.94814,-73.139334&amp;sspn=0.020648,0.029526&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;ll=40.835632,-73.439484&amp;spn=0.661847,0.944824&amp;z=10&amp;om=1" target="_blank">Google Maps direction</a> from JFK airport to All Souls' Church, then to Old Field Club
</li><li>Limo service: despite the name, it is similar to airporter in Canada. Need advance reservation. (a) <a href="http://www.classictrans.com/Pages/airport.html" target="_blank">Classic Limo</a>, around $55 one-way from <a href="http://www.panynj.gov/CommutingTravel/airports/html/kennedy.html" target="_blank">JFK</a> or <a href="http://www.panynj.gov/CommutingTravel/airports/html/laguardia.html" target="_blank">LGA</a> airports to Stony Brook. (b) Spartan Limo: 631-928-5454.
</li><li>Train: No trains are available for LGA; must take limo. For JFK, take an airtrain at JFK to Jamaica, then take <a href="http://www.mta.nyc.ny.us/lirr" target="_blank">L.I.R.R</a> from Jamaica to Stony Brook. Fare is less than $15 one-way, here is <a href="http://www.mta.nyc.ny.us/lirr/html/ttn/stonybro.htm" target="_blank">train to Stony Brook schedule</a>.
</li><li>Taxi: never took one. Over $100 one-way. Maybe last resort?
</li></ul>

